cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper deals with image processing and classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also introduces a new transform method, which involves the use of cumulative distribution, which is related to information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the properties of the new transform and its ability to simplify image representation, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper applies the new transform to image classification, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
